[{"id":"be1b6951d5642118ff8aacef726ade2b","from":"Lesley Groff","from_email":"lesley@nysgllc.com","to":"J. Epstein","to_list":[{"name":"J. Epstein","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"RE: Jeffrey Epstein documents","date":"2008-03-01T18:54:58.000Z","formatted_date":"Mar 1, 2008","formatted_time":"6:54 PM","body":"I'll tell him.\n \n \n \n \n \n \nLesley Groff\nExecutive Assistant to Jeffrey Epstein\n \n \n\n________________________________\n\nFrom: J. Epstein [mailto:jeeproject@yahoo.com] \nSent: Saturday, March 01, 2008 1:13 PM\nTo: Lesley Groff\nSubject: Re: Jeffrey Epstein documents\n\n\nyes\n\n\n----- Original Message ----\nFrom: Lesley Groff <lesley@nysgllc.com>\nTo: J. Epstein <jeeproject@yahoo.com>\nSent: Saturday, March 1, 2008 9:03:53 AM\nSubject: FW: Jeffrey Epstein documents\n\n\n \n \n \n \n \n \n \nLesley Groff\nExecutive Assistant to Jeffrey Epstein\n \n \n\n________________________________\n\nFrom: Eddie Mendoza [mailto:eddie@spaethcom.com] \nSent: Friday, February 29, 2008 6:48 PM\nTo: Lesley Groff\nSubject: RE: Jeffrey Epstein documents\n\n\n\nHello Lesley,\n\nI have a quick question for you. Mr. Epstein paid the $1,900 for\nJanuary's consulting hours and also sent us an additional $5,000. Did he\nmean for us to count February's consulting hours against that $5,000?\n\n \n\nEddie\n\n \n\n \n\n________________________________\n\nFrom: Merrie Spaeth \nSent: Friday, February 29, 2008 5:43 PM\nTo: Lesley Groff\nCc: Eddie Mendoza\nSubject: RE: Jeffrey Epstein documents\n\n \n\nThank you!\n\n \n\n________________________________\n\nFrom: Lesley Groff [mailto:lesley@nysgllc.com] \nSent: Friday, February 29, 2008 5:26 PM\nTo: Merrie Spaeth\nSubject: RE: Jeffrey Epstein documents\n\n \n\nYOu are welcome!  Glad the meeting went well...and I will find out about\nthe forwarding!\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n \n\nLesley Groff\n\nExecutive Assistant to Jeffrey Epstein\n\n \n\n \n\n \n\n________________________________\n\nFrom: Merrie Spaeth [mailto:merrie@spaethcom.com] \nSent: Friday, February 29, 2008 6:32 PM\nTo: Lesley Groff\nCc: Margee Best\nSubject: FW: Jeffrey Epstein documents\n\nLeslie - thanks for arranging everything. Please extend my thanks to\nJeffrey. It was a fascinating session, and I hope he found it useful.\nThis document notes a cc to Jay Lefkowitz and Ken Starr, but I have not\nforwarded it to them. Does Jeffrey want me to send it to them? Does he\nwant to review it first?\n\nBest regards,\n\nMerrie\n\n \n\n________________________________\n\nFrom: Eddie Mendoza \nSent: Friday, February 29, 2008 2:44 PM\nTo: Merrie Spaeth\nSubject: Jeffrey Epstein documents\n\n \n\nMerrie,\n\nHere are the cleaned up and completed documents for your day with\nJeffrey Epstein. Do you want to send them or would you like for me to\nsend them?\n\n \n\n \n\nEddie Mendoza\n\nAdministrative Associate\n\nSpaeth Communications, Inc.\n\n3405 Oak Grove Avenue\n\nDallas, TX 75204\n\noffice: 214-871-8888\n\nfax: 214-871-9015\n\neddie@spaethcom.com\n\nwww.spaethcom.com <http://www.spaethcom.com/> \n\n \n\n\n","body_html":"<!DOCTYPE HTML PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD HTML 4.0 Transitional//EN\">\n<HTML><HEAD>\n<META http-equiv=Content-Type content=\"text/html; charset=us-ascii\">\n<STYLE type=text/css>DIV {\n\tMARGIN: 0px\n}\n</STYLE>\n\n<META content=\"MSHTML 6.00.3790.94\" name=GENERATOR></HEAD>\n<BODY>\n<DIV dir=ltr align=left><SPAN class=317525418-01032008><FONT face=Arial \ncolor=#0000ff size=2>I'll tell him.</FONT></SPAN></DIV>\n<DIV>&nbsp;</DIV>\n<DIV align=left><FONT face=Arial size=2></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>\n<DIV align=left><FONT face=Arial size=2></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>\n<DIV align=left><FONT face=Arial size=2></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>\n<DIV align=left><FONT face=Arial size=2></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>\n<DIV align=left><FONT face=Arial size=2></FONT>&nbsp;</DIV>\n<DIV align=left><FONT face=Arial size=2>Lesley Groff</FONT></DIV>\n<DIV align=left><FONT face=Arial size=2>Executive Assistant to Jeffrey \nEpstein</FONT></DIV>\n<DIV align=lef